comments[11]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-02-18T00:02:31.554Z",cursor-agent,"Evidence: pnpm test passed (19 tests across unit+integration). pnpm test:coverage passed with 100% statements/branches/functions/lines for the enforced release-hardening scope. Integration tests use withTempPmPath and spawn node dist/cli.js with PM_PATH/PM_AUTHOR/PM_SESSION sandbox env values."
  "2026-02-18T00:14:47.650Z",cursor-agent,"Removed linked pnpm test and pnpm test:coverage commands from test-all orchestration scope to avoid recursive invocation chains (integration suite itself exercises test-all)."
  "2026-02-18T01:37:30.396Z",agent,"Planned change-set: add integration assertion that pm test-all exits with code 5 when any linked test command fails, preserving sandbox PM_PATH behavior and deterministic output contract."
  "2026-02-18T01:38:02.209Z",agent,"Implemented integration coverage for test-all dependency-failed semantics: added a mixed pass/fail sandbox scenario asserting exit code 5 and failure aggregation fields in tests/integration/cli.integration.spec.ts."
  "2026-02-18T01:39:39.766Z",agent,"Evidence: pm test pm-912 --run --timeout 480 --json passed both linked commands (sandboxed integration + sandboxed coverage). Coverage remained 100% statements/branches/functions/lines with 26/26 tests passing. Regression sweep via pm test-all --status in_progress --timeout 600 --json passed totals items=5 linked_tests=9 passed=9 failed=0 skipped=0."
  "2026-02-18T02:33:42.999Z",steve,"Planned change-set: enforce sandbox-safe linked test execution by default for pm test --run/test-all and align README/AGENTS examples to use node scripts/run-tests.mjs commands."
  "2026-02-18T02:35:22.295Z",steve,"Implemented change-set: updated README/AGENTS test-link examples to use node scripts/run-tests.mjs, added automatic temp PM_PATH+PM_GLOBAL_PATH sandboxing for linked test command execution in src/commands/test.ts, and expanded unit/integration coverage to verify sandbox env propagation and README contract alignment."
  "2026-02-18T02:38:20.753Z",steve,"Follow-up fix: initialize the ephemeral sandbox PM_PATH before executing linked commands so existing CLI-based linked tests (e.g., node dist/cli.js list-open --json) still run successfully inside isolation."
  "2026-02-18T02:43:05.005Z",steve,"Evidence: node dist/cli.js test pm-912 --run --timeout 900 --json passed all 3 linked commands (coverage + integration + unit). Coverage remained 100% statements/branches/functions/lines (43/43 tests). Regression sweep node dist/cli.js test-all --status in_progress --timeout 900 --json passed totals items=5 linked_tests=10 passed=10 failed=0 skipped=0 after sandbox-init compatibility fix for CLI-linked tests."
  "2026-02-18T02:49:51.727Z",maintainer-agent,"Planned change-set: align README testing policy with implemented integration sandbox env requirements by documenting PM_SESSION alongside PM_PATH and PM_AUTHOR, and enforce this contract in help-readme integration tests."
  "2026-02-18T02:53:01.442Z",maintainer-agent,"Implemented change-set: README testing policy now documents PM_SESSION for integration subprocesses, and tests/integration/help-readme-contract.spec.ts now enforces that contract section. Evidence: node dist/cli.js test pm-912 --run --timeout 900 --json passed all linked tests; node dist/cli.js test-all --status in_progress --timeout 900 --json passed totals items=5 linked_tests=10 passed=10 failed=0 skipped=0; coverage remained 100 percent statements/branches/functions/lines; pnpm build passed."
